@node Vorwort "Welcome"



@{code}@{jcenter}@{fg shine}@{b}Welcome to the Oliver Tacke & Heinz Andreolla-Icons@{ub}@{fg text}

@{jleft}
   Hello, guys!

   Here we are with a collection of icons.
   This time our icons come along in the "GlowIcons" style because
   these icons might adorn the AmigaOS 3.5?!

   We hope that you will like them. If "yes" feel free to write us.

   Have fun

   See you in Cologne,


   Oliver Tacke & Heinz Andreolla
@endnode

@node Config "notes (system requirements)"

   1. An AGA or gfx board AMIGA with Kickstart/Workbench 2.0 or higher.

   2. Screenmode with at least 64 colours, better 256 colours.

   3. Installed NewIcon System.

   4. Proportional square pixel screenmode
      (e.g. 640x480, 800x600 etc.).
@endnode

@node Archiv "archive's contents"

  @{b}@{u} contents of this archive: @{uu}@{ub}


   1. 02 GUIDE files (English and German)

   2. 48 Icons for Applications

   3. 69 DockIcons

   4. 50 programme drawers

   5. 52 drawers with letters

   6. 05 JPG pictures
   
   7. 03 miscellaneous

   8. !! more will follow

@endnode
@node Rechtliches "Copyright..."

@{code}@{jcenter}@{fg shine}in general@{fg text}

@{jleft}
     These small pictures may not be published as long as there is no
     OS3.5 available

     All parts of this collection and the documentation must stay together.
     Publishing only excerpts is not allowed.

     We are not responsible for any damage or misuse of any kind.
     But certainly this archive is not meant for use in OS1.3. (We just
     wanted to tell you...)

     If you really like this collection we'd like you to tell others. We'd
     like to get feedback.

     The design of the icons should remind you of the "GlowIcon" style
     in order to create a uniform look of the Workbench.

@{code}@{jcenter}@{fg shine}Copyright@{fg text}

@{jleft}
     GlowIcons ® by @{" Oliver & Heinz " Link GI}
@ENDNODE

